				<div class="postbody">
				When it crashes does it give an error?
<br />

<br />
I agree sounds like a video issue, have the latest drivers?
<br />
Just for the heck of it, try running it as opengl.  Add under your program properties:
<br />
"C:\Program Files\World of Warcraft\WoW.exe" -opengl 
<br />

<br />
For me that caused problems.  But who knows, maybe that mode it'll run smoother for you.
<br />

<br />
Does it effect you when your running in windowed mode?  Try that too I guess.
<br />

<br />

